    chronologyEn: [
      'Emperor Tang Taizong commissions the monk Xuanzang (Sanzang) to fetch the Buddhist scriptures from the West.',
      'Guanyin frees Sun Wukong from the Five Elements Mountain to become Sanzang\'s first disciple.',
      'Zhu Bajie and Sha Wujing, two gods banished from Heaven, are recruited as the second and third disciples.',
